# <%= @app %>

A [shaolin](https://github.com/mantissa-lab/shaolin) CQRS/Event-Sourcing backend.

## Develop

```bash
bundle install
bundle exec shaolin g module users   # scaffold a module
bundle exec shaolin server           # serve on http://localhost:8080
```

## Deploy (container-native, GCP-first)

```bash
docker build -t <%= @app %> .
# HTTP service -> Cloud Run / Knative:
kubectl apply -f deploy/service.yaml
```

See `AGENTS.md` for how the codebase is organized and how to work in it.
